HTML5 Image Sample
==================

This is a sample application used by an article for the Mobage Developer's blog [article](https://mobage-developers.squarespace.com/blog/2014/6/16/of-the-html5-game-until-can-do-it-3).

This applications uses [an W3C HTML5 Logo](http://www.w3.org/html/logo/downloads/HTML5_Logo_256.png) provided under [Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
